

This simple python code uses the Adafruit BBIO library. First install it on
your BBB using the instructions found here

http://learn.adafruit.com/setting-up-io-python-library-on-beaglebone-black

You can then run this demo to exercise all the functions on the cape.

root@bbb-w:~/checkout# python demo.py

